<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787594>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Aquattuor spp. A. A. stereosathe Enghoff sp. nov., paratype, front end. B–C. A. udzungwensis Enghoff sp. nov., paratype, telson, lateral and posterior view. D–E. A. udzungwensis Enghoff sp. nov., limbus. D. Specimen from West Kilombero Scarp FR. E. Paratype. Scale bars: A–D = 0.1 mm; E = 0.01 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3787594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3787604>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Aquattuor udzungwensis Enghoff sp. nov. A–B, D. Paratype. C. Specimen from West Kilombero Scarp FR. A. Gonopods in situ. B. Telopodite, ventral view. C. Right gonopod, anterior view. D. Telomere tip. li = lateral incision; pa = palette; mpl = mesal-posterior lamella of telomere. Scale bars: A–C = 0.1 mm; D = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3787604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

